<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Concert Stage1 Extract</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/seatmap-concert-stage1.css">
</head>
<body>
<header class="top">
    <div class="brand">
        <span class="logo">▦</span>
        <span>Concert Stage1</span>
        <small>단색 도면 추출</small>
    </div>

    <div class="top-actions">
        <!-- 필요하면 프로젝트 매핑에 맞게 href만 수정 -->
        <a class="top-btn" href="/admin/seatmap/main">이전</a>
        <a class="top-btn top-btn--primary" href="/admin/seatmap/concert/stage2">Stage2</a>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="work">
    <aside class="side">
        <p class="side-title">Stage1 · 파트 분리</p>

        <div class="tabs">
            <button type="button" class="tab active" id="tab1">파트1 자르기</button>
            <button type="button" class="tab" id="tab2">파트2 색상</button>
            <button type="button" class="tab" id="tab3">파트3 다듬기</button>
        </div>

        <section id="part1">
            <div class="box active">
                <h3>파트 1 - 자르기</h3>

                <button type="button" class="btn btn--dark" id="cropStart">범위 드래그 시작</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn" id="cropApply" disabled>선택 범위로 자르기</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary" id="go2">다음: 색상 추출</button>

                <div class="help">
                    도면 영역만 남기고 제목/범례/여백은 제거하세요.
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="part2" class="hidden">
            <div class="box active">
                <h3>파트 2 - 색상 선택 추출</h3>

                <div class="help">
                    오른쪽 이미지를 클릭하면 해당 색상이 추가되고 즉시 미리보기에 반영됩니다.
                    원본은 선명하게 두고 선택된 도형 영역만 위에 덮어 표시합니다.
                </div>

                <div id="samples"></div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div>
                        <label for="tol">색상 허용 범위</label>
                        <input type="range" id="tol" min="5" max="120" value="45">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="alpha">도형 표시 강도</label>
                        <input type="range" id="alpha" min="0" max="100" value="55">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div>
                        <label for="shapeColor">도형색</label>
                        <input type="color" id="shapeColor" value="#d9d9d9">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="bgColor">배경색</label>
                        <input type="color" id="bgColor" value="#f7f7f7">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div>
                        <label for="hole">숫자/구멍 메우기</label>
                        <input type="number" id="hole" value="140">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="viewMode">보기</label>
                        <select id="viewMode">
                            <option value="mix">원본+미리보기</option>
                            <option value="clean">미리보기만</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <button type="button" class="btn" id="clearSamples">색상 초기화</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn" id="restoreOriginal">원본 복구</button>
                </div>

                <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary" id="go3">다음: 다듬기</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="part3" class="hidden">
            <div class="box active">
                <h3>파트 3 - 다듬기</h3>

                <div class="row">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn--dark" id="eraser">지우개 사용</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn" id="stopEraser">지우개 종료</button>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn--green" id="rectFill">브러쉬 채우기</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn" id="stopRectFill">채우기 종료</button>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div>
                        <label for="eraserSize">지우개/브러쉬 크기</label>
                        <input type="range" id="eraserSize" min="4" max="80" value="18">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="cleanupArea">작은 조각 제거</label>
                        <input type="number" id="cleanupArea" value="180">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn--amber" id="cleanup">작은 선/조각 자동 제거</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn" id="restoreExtract">추출본 복구</button>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn--green" id="saveClean">Stage1 저장</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary" id="toStage3">Stage2 이동</button>
                </div>

                <div class="help">
                    숫자 때문에 비어 보이는 부분은 <b>브러쉬 채우기</b>로 드래그해서 메우세요.
                    실제 좌석 버튼이 아니라 Stage2 도면용 회색 사각형입니다.
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </aside>

    <main class="main">
        <div class="canvas-wrap">
            <div class="canvas-head">
                <span id="title">원본 / 자르기</span>
                <span id="size">-</span>
            </div>

            <div class="canvas-box" id="box">
                <canvas class="base" id="canvas"></canvas>
                <canvas id="overlay"></canvas>
                <div id="eraserCursor" class="eraser-cursor"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>

<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<script src="/js/admin/seatmap-concert-stage1.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
